reviews.text: This restaurant has changed name focusing on Japanese stream pot. The staff are quite nice and no hard selling. The food quality is standard as a small Chinese family business but the portion is big. The price is quite low comparatively. No 10% charges nor tips.

Not bad given its price and location
Kids friendly!
Best food we've eaten in Cheung Chau

reviews.text: 和家人去長洲遊玩，見這裏午餐連飲品價錢合理就入去醫肚了。食材及味道方面很一般，煮法也是港式日本料理，份量夠但沒有驚喜喔！
價錢大眾化,但食物質數高😁😁😁
很值得去的一間餐廳，牛肉鍋是一定要試！
不错的日本料理，價錢適中，款式颇多，有日本火鍋。
